    <text id="A1424T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Hite informs his correspondent that they have moved to a new prisoner of war camp
                    and requests money.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1864-07-07">July 7<hi rend="super"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> 1864</date>
                        <name type="place"><orig reg="Prisoners'">Prisoner<hi rend="super">s</hi></orig>
                            Camp, Elmira <abbr expan="New York">N. Y.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute/>
                </opener>

                <p>I <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> you a letter Some time ago and as I have not
                    received an answer I will write again I am very well at this time and I hope
                    that <orig reg="those">thoes</orig> few lines may reach you and find you and
                    family all enjoying good health we camp here yesterday we are all highly pleased
                    with our exchange of prisons and I think we will get along very well <del
                        hand="h1">we</del>
                    <add hand="h1" place="inline">now</add> I <del hand="h1">are</del>
                    <add hand="h1" place="inline">am</add> in need of Some things that we do not
                    expect to get without money you would confer a great favor by sending me Some
                    money I hope to hear from you soon Direct your letter to John N. Hite. Prisoner
                    of War. Elmira <abbr expan="New York">N.Y.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="number">No</abbr> 30. Barracks <abbr expan="number">No</abbr> 3.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute/>
                    <signed>John N. Hite</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
